  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Twin Rooms </strong>sleep up to four people (extra beds are bunk beds) and have a TV, safe, shower or bath and hairdryer. Twin rooms for sole use are available for a supplement and available on request. Please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Twin Rooms</strong> sleep up to four people. They have a balcony with mountain views.</p>
<p><strong>The Luxor Suite </strong>is very spacious at 35m² and sleeps up to two people. It's spread over two floors and the top floor is in a turret. The floors are linked by a spiral staircase. It also has a mini-bar and jacuzzi bath. The suite is available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> are available with no supplement.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
